column2: SELECT   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.objID, s.z as zphot, s.zErr, s.absMagU, s.absMagG, s.absMagR, s.absMagI, s.absMagZ,s.photoErrorClass FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN Photoz AS s ON s.objID = p.objid  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN ON s.objID = GN.objID
